<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.5">
<l>tūṇā yataṉū ṭariyāy vantutōṉṟi</l>
<l>pēṇā vavuṇa ṉuṭalam piḷantiṭṭāy</l>
<l>cēṇār tiruvēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>kōṇā kaṇaiyāy kuṟikkoḷ ḷeṉainīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a pillar [and] as a lion coming and appearing from within it,</l>
<l>You who split asunder the body of the insolent demon,</l>
<l>You whose bed is a powerful serpent [and] who dwells</l>
<l>On the lofty mountain Tiruvēnkaṭam, you [should] guard me carefully.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
